title: Slow-Cooked Beef Brisket & Parmesan Mash for Dinner with Pear & Chocolate Chip Crumble for Dessert
description: There’s no rush to make this delectable dinner when it barely takes any time but it will look like it took you all day. With pre-slow-cooked beef brisket drizzled in a red wine jus and balanced with sweet honey glazed carrots to add colour and flavour, this dish
will amaze everyone at the table.
